            "chapter": 101,
            "verse": 1,
            "text": "The striking calamity"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 101,
            "verse": 2,
            "text": "What is the striking calamity"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 101,
            "verse": 3,
            "text": "And how would you know what is the striking calamity"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 101,
            "verse": 4,
            "text": "It is the Day when the human beings will be like dispersed moths"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 101,
            "verse": 5,
            "text": "and the mountains will be like fluffed up wool"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 101,
            "verse": 6,
            "text": "and then, the one whose scales are heavy [with good deeds]"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 101,
            "verse": 7,
            "text": "will have a pleasant life"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 101,
            "verse": 8,
            "text": "but the one whose scales are light"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 101,
            "verse": 9,
            "text": "his refuge will be an abyss"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 101,
            "verse": 10,
            "text": "And what will convey to you what that is"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 101,
            "verse": 11,
            "text": "a Raging Fire"
        }
    ]
}